CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: LA Rosa Holdings Corp is a holding company for five agent-centric, technology-integrated, cloud-based, multi-service real estate companies. It conducts its operations through five subsidiaries: La Rosa Coaching, LLC, which is engaged in the coaching, training and education of its real estate agents at every phase of the real estate business; La Rosa CRE, LLC, which is a commercial real estate brokerage where it represent buyers and sellers in the sale of commercial real estate; La Rosa Franchising, LLC, which is engaged in the sale, oversight, and provision of operating systems of independently owned and operated franchises of La Rosa Realty as well and the ongoing training and support for the franchise owners and staff; La Rosa Property Management, LLC, which is engaged in providing training, compliance, support and accounting services for La Rosa Realty agents, and La Rosa Realty, LLC, which is engaged in the residential real estate brokerage business.
